{"tid":1442431,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"係時候傾set deadline再行動升級","createTime":"2019-08-11T03:09:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T16:49:44.000Z","uid":278288,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"326a2ad688de3c751bab329122a70bcd619d7205","tid":1442431,"uid":278288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:09:33.000Z","msg":"經過8月5，近期最大型行動之後，大家好似失去咗方向<br />\n因為接收嘅資訊量太多，我地好容易俾啲支線轉移咗視線<br />\n大家嘅討論重點變咗某一兩單嘅濫捕案？某一兩次地區遊行嘅作戰方向？某一兩個屋苑點對抗犬隻？<br />\n<br />\n雖然遍地開花係重要，但暫時嚟睇冇辦法施加更大壓力俾政府<br />\n另外，政府陰招愈嚟愈多，愈嚟愈多鬼混入損害我地聲譽，同時分化同路人<br />\n我地係時候回歸我地6、7月嘅做法：set deadline，政府唔回應再升級行動<br />\n<br />\n再升級行動可能又要擺脫一啲底線<br />\n抗爭為市民帶來不便係無可避免<br />\n有影響先有壓力<br />\n事前文宣必需做足，市民要知道我地已經比咗足夠時間政府回應<br />\n<br />\n建議行動：<br />\n1.同時圍堵政府局同署headquarter office接放工，包括政總、稅局、各區政府合署等，癱瘓政府運作<br />\n<br />\n2.再次connect航空界，癱瘓機場<br />\n<br />\n3.吹雞搞多次大型遊行，集中一個地區，鼓勵大家集中製作侮辱習近平嘅poster，激死中共<br />\n<br />\n3.再次大三罷，連續兩日<br />\n<br />\n4.weekend一連兩日揀旅遊景點多方集會，目標如廣東道、金紫荊廣場等，最好令中共自遊行都cut埋<br />\n<br />\n面對政府經濟牌，我認為需要學習民間記者會嘅答法，將責任歸究示威者係倒果為因<br />\n我地係懇請政府立即回應五大訴求，否則迫於無奈行動升級<br />\n<br />\n希望大家對下一步升級行動同deadline俾多啲意見"},{"pid":"50e5edc3e27d5f0fce5196bbc9076742cee83515","tid":1442431,"uid":278288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:11:09.000Z","msg":"希望大家除咗戰術都討論下大型行動可以點升級"},{"pid":"66664627197e6ba062c75276dfa2656c9409a5f4","tid":1442431,"uid":260036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:11:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SmCSzTz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSmCSzTz.jpg&h=12efb6e8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LmSGtdA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLmSGtdA.jpg&h=d8a1db8d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9fb77b81bb2d243803297d60e6efd8a02a603205","tid":1442431,"uid":278288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:12:07.000Z","msg":"唔好俾政府拖字闕拖死"},{"pid":"f69ec5db15f48cb53055f3ba7580e6947d7aeddb","tid":1442431,"uid":278288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:12:23.000Z","msg":"香港人不再政治冷感"},{"pid":"b87cbba06d1e2a4d7fbce7ffeb12ab8f9c236edd","tid":1442431,"uid":278288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:14:08.000Z","msg":"好多人話香港人好善忘，其實我地只係用5年沉澱當年失敗嘅傷痛<br />\n我地從未遺忘，我地今次係要贏"},{"pid":"4c8cc4ca5acc7a90d6156ed7a556797a0a0bf81c","tid":1442431,"uid":278288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:14:45.000Z","msg":"襯未出街討論吓吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82a6123fefb6b7c88a294950a8d45b0589c92f34","tid":1442431,"uid":278288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:15:25.000Z","msg":"政府識轉陣<br />\n我地識變招"},{"pid":"60aef6cef6002a42ba6144368e2f2298c25374e6","tid":1442431,"uid":278288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:15:50.000Z","msg":"你有張良計<br />\n我有過場梯"},{"pid":"4d68d9f029ccc750f128e33137a3951b37c559ef","tid":1442431,"uid":278288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:20:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8564d49385cd7feea0653de520d9defab66bbc81","tid":1442431,"uid":278288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:25:19.000Z","msg":"自推1"},{"pid":"851d2707c46ffb6b4145af0268f42899ee95f8e0","tid":1442431,"uid":229886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:25:41.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"6b1bd10c6db1ce040f3eafb311f0358e1b8f9185","tid":1442431,"uid":267342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:32:39.000Z","msg":"第四點唔太認同，自由行要照黎我地要照宣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d84ba718cc5debddcda31190497ccd12f4dc0523","tid":1442431,"uid":2